Classic OmniScript Designer

Create OmniScripts in the classic designer when an element, property, or functionality solves a project requirement that you cannot resolve in the LWC OmniScript Designer.

It is possible to switch between the classic and LWC OmniScript designers. The classic OmniScript designer is built in Angular and provides a limited view of the OmniScript during configuration. The LWC OmniScript Designer provides in-product help and a user-friendly canvas that enables users to preview the appearance of an OmniScript while configuring elements.

Getting Started with OmniScripts
Vlocity OmniScript is an omnichannel customer engagement and a business tool built on the Salesforce platform. Administrators can define a script once and then deploy the script within a Salesforce application or on a web page.
